title: Alex Rodriguez and Pete Rose Bond over Getting Booed
text:
Alex Rodriguez and Pete Rose Bond over Getting Booed Bleacher Report 6 hrs ago Thomas Duffy © Yahoo Alex Rodriguez and Pete Rose are no strangers to boo birds.
AdChoices While on set Monday for Fox's coverage of the MLB postseason, A-Rod and the Hit King shared a fist bump after the New York Yankees designated hitter noted just how qualified he is in getting hated on:
"I have a PHD in getting booed."- @AROD #ALCSonFS1 #postseason
— FOX Sports: MLB (@MLBONFOX) October 20, 2015 The ultimate bro moment between two baseball exiles, or the beginning of an evil empire?
